data.description: Don't miss seeing this charming home in the Amberdale/Oakridge neighborhood of Lumberton. This home is a 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home that has been well taken care of. A new backyard fence was just installed giving privacy to the very large backyard, there is lots of potential for a pool to be added, etc. Granite countertops in the kitchen and bathrooms, large walk in closets, a bonus room above the garage, formal dining area, hardwood flooring in living spaces, moisture barrier underneath the home - an all around wonderful home! Schedule your showing to see this home today.
